**Egg Hunter** | Unaligned Killing | Joke Role
__Basics:__
Throughout Easter, the Egg Hunter searches for easter eggs. 
__Advanced__;
The easter eggs hide in many forms and can be hidden via various means throughout the server.
The Egg Hunter must notify event hosts when they've found an easter egg in order to collect it. 
The Egg Hunter knows that there is at least 20 easter eggs to find during easter.
The Egg Hunter wins by finding more eggs than any other Egg Hunter, or be tied for the most. Sharing easter egg locations is forbidden.
